stand that running a business is a time consuming effort, so it was important for us to offer the necessary tools to organize and optimize the sales process, within a simple interface that takes minutes (not hours) to set up. We don\'t try to be everything to everyone, and today when we look at other CRM solutions, it is clear that they do, and the result is a convoluted interface that serves few. \r\n\r\nWhat we have found is that our software is helping many businesses who need to streamline their sales process, coordinate team members and maintain critical customer relationships. \r\n\r\nI hope that RainLeads helps your business as much as I\'ve seen it organize our own sales efforts. Now, go make it rain!\"  <i>--Fuchsia McInerney, CEO</i>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>OUR TEAM</b>\r\n\r\n<b>Founder</b> | Fuchsia McInerney \r\n\r\n<b>Software Developer</b> | Luc Vachon\r\n\r\n<b>Web Developer</b>| Kurt Vachon\r\n\r\n<b>Web Developer</b> | Richard Medeiros\r\n\r\n<b>Application Developer</b> | Chad Kaufman\r\n\r\n<b>Account Manager</b> | Susan Dodge\r\n\r\n<b>Account Manager</b> | Makanga Njagi\r\n\r\n\r\n','About RainLeads',''),('RTFemail_daily_digest',1357824344,'Hello %receiver,\r\n\r\nHere\'s a summary of your lead activity for %accountname. For more detail, log into your account at <a href=\'%homeurl\'>%homeurl</a>. \r\n\r\n%post\r\n\r\nRegards, \r\nThe %sitename Team\r\n<a href=\'%homeurl\'>%homeurl</a>\r\n\r\nTo manage your notifications, log in and go to your Admin Settings. ','Your %sitename Daily Digest for %accountname',''),('RTFemail_new_lead',1357824359,'Hello %receiver,\r\n\r\nYou have just received a new lead into your %sitename account:\r\n\r\n%post\r\n\r\nView the full form entry at: %url\r\n\r\nRegards, \r\nThe %sitename Team\r\n<a href=\"%homeurl\">%homeurl</a>\r\n\r\nTo manage your notifications, log in and go to your Admin Settings. ','New Lead Received ',''),('RTFemail_event_reminder',1357824375,'This is the reminder you requested from %sitename about the f